      "content": { "text": "We redesigned one SaaS checkout flow.\n\nConversion went 3.1% -> 4.6% in three weeks. No new features. Just UX.\n\nHere's the exact teardown 🧵\n\n1/ The old flow asked for billing before the user saw value...\n2/ We moved the 'aha' moment ahead of the form...\n3/ One field per screen beat the single long form by 31%...", "media_type": "text", "media_count": 0, "is_thread": true, "thread_len": 8, "has_link": false, "post_type": "original" },
